Title: Eagle Eye, Eagle Die
Description:
The eagles out by the undersea have bathed in the light of Beledar, and it makes them particularly tasty.

Could you get a few eagle fillets? Take this harpoon with you, they can be feisty.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Auralia Steelstrike at the Steelstrike Home in Mereldar.
CompletionText: Watch yourself. The eagles can easily injure you.
RewardText:
These look very juicy. Thank you, $n!

I'll ensure that these go towards a good meal for us.
